        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/us-global-reputation-decline-trump-return.png" alt="The United States is becoming less popular globally in the aftermath of Donald Trump‚Äôs return to the White House" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i> The United States is becoming less popular globally in the aftermath of Donald Trump‚Äôs return to the White House. Credits: Getty Images</i></p>
